casebody.data:
Abdu Qaaliq Ibn ISMAIL
v.
STATE of North Carolina. No. 634P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 5, 2005. Abdu Qaaliq Ismail, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Kenneth W. Honeycutt, District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 21st day of December 2004 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Union County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th day of February 2005."
